---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="最新资讯">
  <section class="pt-20 pb-20 px-4 md:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-center mb-12">最新资讯</h1>

      <!-- 分类标签 -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center mb-12">
        <button class="px-6 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full hover:bg-blue-700 transition">全部</button>
        <button class="px-6 py-2 glass-button rounded-full">招生录取</button>
        <button class="px-6 py-2 glass-button rounded-full">校园新闻</button>
        <button class="px-6 py-2 glass-button rounded-full">移民政策</button>
        <button class="px-6 py-2 glass-button rounded-full">就业实习</button>
        <button class="px-6 py-2 glass-button rounded-full">申请更新</button>
      </div>

      <!-- 新闻列表 -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map((i) => (
          <article class="apple-card hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
              <div class="md:w-1/4">
                <div class="w-full h-40 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-purple-400 rounded-lg"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="md:w-3/4">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full">招生录取</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">2024年7月{10 + i}日</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">重要资讯标题 {i}</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                  这是一条重要的大学资讯摘要。点击了解更多关于各大学的招生政策、录取情况、移民政策或就业实习信息...
                </p>
                <a href="#" class="inline-block text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-semibold">阅读全文 →</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- 高亮资讯模块 -->
      <div class="mt-16">
        <h2 class="mb-8">热门话题</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="apple-card bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-50">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">🎓 美国大学录取数据更新</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              最新的美国名校录取数据显示，今年的录取率再次创下新低。Harvard、Stanford 等学校的录取率持续下降...
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-semibold">了解更多</a>
          </div>

          <div class="apple-card bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-emerald-50">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">🌍 英国签证政策调整</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              英国政府最近宣布了新的国际学生签证政策，影响申请时间表和费用...
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-semibold">了解更多</a>
          </div>

          <div class="apple-card bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-red-50">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">💼 实习机会指南</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              顶尖大学和科技公司最新的实习项目信息，包括申请截止日期和要求...
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-semibold">了解更多</a>
          </div>

          <div class="apple-card bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">📋 2024年标化考试日期</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              SAT、ACT、GRE、GMAT 等标化考试最新的考试日期和注册信息...
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-semibold">了解更多</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 订阅通讯 -->
      <div class="mt-16 apple-card bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-purple-50 text-center">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">订阅我们的通讯</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">获取最新的大学资讯、申请技巧和政策更新</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-3 max-w-md mx-auto">
          <input type="email" placeholder="输入你的邮箱..." class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 border border-white/30 rounded-lg bg-white/50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" />
          <button class="px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition font-semibold">
            订阅
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
